reviewText: i will admit that i love these videos of naked men frolicking around with other men, acting like i think Eden would have been. i don't like porn, and i don't think these films are that. they are dreams of innocent loving man to man and enjoying each others company in wonderfully natural places. i have several of these films now and i like that they are wordless but not quite silent and every body is beautiful and all their friends are with them and every body loves each other. it isn't like bar pickups and they don't look sick. it is a pure gay fantasy.
